# 2.9.0/

Release documentation and artifacts for Intent v2.9.0 (Agentic Software Engineering Suite). This release introduces rules as first-class citizens, a critic-<lang> subagent family for code review, and a user extension system at ~/.intent/ext/.

## Files

- `RELEASE_NOTES.md` -- Overview of v2.9.0 features, rules library, critic subagents, extension system, breaking changes, and upgrade path
